Me ajude!

311
00:40:37,080 --> 00:40:38,320
Ei, mãe...

312
00:40:38,570 --> 00:40:41,520
Posso ir brincar com o Ken hoje? 

313
00:40:42,440 --> 00:40:44,460
Ei, Takashi! Diga oi primeiro! 

314
00:40:48,180 --> 00:40:49,490
