335
00:42:36,520 --> 00:42:37,430
Entendi.

336
00:42:39,240 --> 00:42:40,270
Mas venha em qualquer circunstância! 

337
00:42:42,910 --> 00:42:43,660
Certo. 

338
00:45:15,580 --> 00:45:16,240
Vamos começar. 

339
00:47:01,170 --> 00:47:01,890
Não! 

340
00:47:02,110 --> 00:47:03,000
Olhe para ela! 

341
00:48:08,270 --> 00:48:09,160
